org.panthercode.arctic.core.processing.modules

Class Bundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.panthercode.arctic.core.processing.modules.AbstractModule
      • org.panthercode.arctic.core.processing.modules.Bundle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Identifiable, Versionable, Module
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Chunk, Process

    public abstract class Bundle
extends AbstractModule
    The bundle class is used to hold and proceed a list of modules. Every module is stored in an internal list.
